    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_5_4151-4217",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4151-4217",
      "markText": "而玛萨·马尔克斯在两场袭击中都安然无恙，他把这归结于圣婴的庇佑。当然，埃斯科瓦尔把玛萨·马尔克斯没能杀死他的奇迹也归功于同一位圣婴。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4151&rangeEnd=4217",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4151&rangeEnd=4217"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_4_534-627",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "534-627",
      "markText": "上车前，她回头看了一眼，确保没人跟踪她。现在是波哥大晚上七点零五分。天色在一小时前黑了下来，国家公园里灯光昏暗，光秃秃的树木在昏暗悲伤的天空的映衬下显得鬼影幢幢，但乍看并没有什么可怕的。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=534&rangeEnd=627",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=534&rangeEnd=627"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_15_14699-14727",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "14699-14727",
      "markText": "“太棒了！”她充满幻想地感叹道，“这一切能写成一本书。”",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=14699&rangeEnd=14727",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=14699&rangeEnd=14727"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_5_3768-3835",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3768-3835",
      "markText": "玛萨将军从七年前的贝利萨里奥·贝坦库尔政府时期就开始担任本职，在比尔希略·巴尔科总统任职期间续任，而且刚刚被塞萨尔·加维里亚总统任命。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3768&rangeEnd=3835",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3768&rangeEnd=3835"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_5_14543-14593",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "14543-14593",
      "markText": "帕丘意识到绑架他的歹徒如此匆忙不仅是出于安全原因，还是为了及时赶回来，收听圣达菲和卡尔达斯的足球赛。",
      "totalCount": 66,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=14543&rangeEnd=14593",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=14543&rangeEnd=14593"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_8_5253-5276",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5253-5276",
      "markText": "埃罗·布斯两米高，一米宽，是个五十岁的青少年。",
      "totalCount": 66,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5253&rangeEnd=5276",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5253&rangeEnd=5276"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_6_13009-13051",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13009-13051",
      "markText": "他们憎恨其他的一切：政客、政府、国家、司法、警察、全社会。他们说，生活就是一坨狗屎。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13009&rangeEnd=13051",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13009&rangeEnd=13051"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_7_5495-5518",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5495-5518",
      "markText": "她出生于一九五〇年三月八日，是冷酷无情的双鱼座",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5495&rangeEnd=5518",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5495&rangeEnd=5518"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_11_1502-1601",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1502-1601",
      "markText": "司法部门并不能做多少事。法官们微薄的工资仅够他们糊口，而不够他们负担孩子的教育费用。他们深陷于没有出路的两难抉择当中：要么被杀，要么被毒贩收买。令人敬佩和痛心的是，许多法官在这种情况下情愿选择死亡。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1502&rangeEnd=1601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1502&rangeEnd=1601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_11_13122-13157",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "13122-13157",
      "markText": "几天后，埃斯科瓦尔给他回信，他的自尊心因为信中的普法课程而受到了伤害。",
      "totalCount": 55,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=13122&rangeEnd=13157",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=13122&rangeEnd=13157"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_5_6693-6741",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6693-6741",
      "markText": "这是难以避免的：在哥伦比亚，所有超过六人的聚会，不论何种类型，不管在什么时段，都注定会变成舞会。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6693&rangeEnd=6741",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6693&rangeEnd=6741"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020485_13_6114-6130",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "6114-6130",
      "markText": "以及难以挽回的结局：突然的死亡。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020485&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6114&rangeEnd=6130",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ef232e50813ab6e80g01546c?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6114&rangeEnd=6130"
    },
    {
